"identifier","text":"directionalShadowMaxDistance"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Double","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowMaxDistance","type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"directionalShadowMaxDistance","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/directionallight3d\/directionalshadowmaxdistance"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/DirectionalLight3D/directionalShadowFadeStart":{"title":"directionalShadowFadeStart","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowFadeStart","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/directionallight3d\/directionalshadowfadestart","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"directionalShadowFadeStart","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Double","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Proportion of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowMaxDistance","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" at which point the shadow starts to fade. At "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowMaxDistance"},{"type":"text","text":", the shadow will disappear. The default value is a balance between smooth fading and distant shadow visibility. If the camera moves fast and the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowMaxDistance","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" is low, consider lowering "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/DirectionalLight3D\/directionalShadowFadeStart","isActive":true},{"text":" below ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0.